name: Make Europe Great Again
description: $MEGA is a memecoin supporting the movement "Make Europe Great Again", a type of spinoff of Donald Trump`s MAGA. The idea is being pushed by Elon Musk and other EU Leaders in the recent months. Calling for change for the European Union. We believe $MEGA can bring about awareness for Europeans wanting change for the future. This token serves as a culture community token, supporting the political movement.
